          C 152.70146,493.47282 288.63461,528.80461 381.26391,662.02535 
          C 468.83815,529.62199 609.82641,489.17075 609.82641,358.71731 
          C 609.82641,292.47731 556.06651,238.7173 489.82641,238.71731 
